title: Bad Dreams {1988}.avi
description: It is the mid-70's. A sinister cult called Unity Fields commits mass suicide in a horrific manner - by fire - at the behest of its psychopathic leader, Harris. Only one young woman named Cynthia survives to tell the tale. Now, 13 years later, Cynthia is having grim reminders of the mass-suicide, as people around her begin to die one at a time. Cynthia finds out quickly that the ghost of Harris is back... to claim his 'love child'.
